{"tid":1905360,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府資助本地製口罩 規定年底前生產不得出口","createTime":"2020-03-01T08:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T08:01:18.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a476f9d186b2116d56039775c60f9c7dbb0751c6","tid":1905360,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T08:01:18.000Z","msg":"政府資助本地製口罩 規定年底前生產不得出口<br />\n<br />\n政府在防疫抗疫基金下，推出本地口罩生產資助計劃，明日起接受申請，每間合資格公司最多可獲500萬元資助，涵蓋生產設備、設置廠房等成本。<br />\n<br />\n計劃規定，申請的公司必須要在年底前開始生產口罩，每月至少50萬個，產量200萬個以下，政府會全數採購，多出來的貨量只能用作本地銷售，不得出口。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1270390&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1270390%26csid%3D261_341&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGotDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=246fa1e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1270390&amp;csid=261_341</a>"}]}